Enriching the security SpEL DSL is actually a bit tricky (I had to copy a Spring protected class to get it working) and should be used when needing more than **R**ole **B**ased **A**ccess **C**ontrol. I have [another tutorial][2] for that, but it is quite adherent to my libs and starters (the previous one I linked is not).

