Thank you, guys. I&#39;ve found a solution. 
I had a config class with following code:

    @Override
    public void addArgumentResolvers(List&lt;HandlerMethodArgumentResolver&gt; argumentResolvers) {
        argumentResolvers.add(new SpecificationArgumentResolver(abstractApplicationContext));
        argumentResolvers.add(new PageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver());
    }

You can see here 

&gt; PageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver

Which I tried to change. I think it was a problem why my other configuration classes didn&#39;t work. 
As I changed that code to: 

    @Override
    public void addArgumentResolvers(List&lt;HandlerMethodArgumentResolver&gt; argumentResolvers) {
        argumentResolvers.add(new SpecificationArgumentResolver(abstractApplicationContext));
        PageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver pageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver = new PageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver();
        pageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver.setMaxPageSize(100_000);
        argumentResolvers.add(pageableHandlerMethodArgumentResolver);
    }

Now everything works fine. Thanks again!

